4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"YO7"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"818d31c1-0911-49e7-86cb-4ef50236e937","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"まあその辺りも含めてまだまだ発展途上の分野と言える","ts":"1579226275.388200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Q5xHt"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1be1bac3-0fa0-4b3e-89d2-94fe6a86a9be","type":"message","user":"UGP5AJKU4","text":"そういえば使っててふと思ったことなんですけど\n\n```import { Query, Headers, Param, Put, Delete, Body, Post } from '@hoge/fuga';```\nとかあって(tsファイル)\n`Put` と `Delete` がunused importだとすると\n\n`:LspNextDiagnostic`\n`dw`\n`:LspNextDiagnostic`\nとすると位置がズレるみたいなのですが、しょうがないんですかね？","ts":"1579230206.002500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"oEAID"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"9cd3d76f-d651-46e7-bc5a-b26acbdf5e07","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"新しい diagnostic が飛んでくるまでは古い diagnostic しかないと思うのでしょうがなさそうですね。","ts":"1579231176.003600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"JxIm"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"0ca6a414-f0c2-4eea-ab41-f73b54c5d1b0","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"2回目の前にLspDocumentDiagnosticやるしかない、的?","ts":"1579231301.004900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"7uOkK"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"daaeaefb-3d14-4d94-bac3-ed4126c5af31","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"同期的にやるなら、ですが","ts":"1579231319.005400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"7l5/"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ec427019-75a1-4611-96bd-fab9b861b303","type":"message","user":"UGP5AJKU4","text":"なるほど、そういうことですよね。\n\nlspのrequest/responseがテキスト編集より速ければ何も違和感は無さそうですが\n時々あれ？となりました","ts":"1579231338.006200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Whp"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"B28F46DC-F2C7-48CA-9F66-146B7D811EEC","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"リアルタイムにやるのなら TextChange とかフックしてぶん投げるしか無さそう…","ts":"1579231353.006700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"OVUda"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"df3e0df0-ab8b-4a35-a55f-ea1939f980f4","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"<@UGP5AJKU4> めちゃくちゃゆっくりやったら意図したとおりに動くんでしょうか？（dw 後に、診断が更新されるまで待ってみるとという意味です。）","ts":"1579231602.007300","thread_ts":"1579231602.007300","reply_count":3,"replies":[{"user":"UGP5AJKU4","ts":"1579231739.007800"},{"user":"U8R597E9H","ts":"1579231910.008000"},{"user":"UGP5AJKU4","ts":"1579232257.008200"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"uG+0"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"5a4beaf2-78b9-477a-8785-d957d129be66","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"diagnostics も時間かかったりしますしね。","ts":"1579231614.007600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zLcQc"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"98a71773-2c32-4d37-aeff-55ccfd7cbcf7","type":"message","user":"UGP5AJKU4","text":"はい、待つとtext positionもちゃんと更新されます。\nすばやくやると時々ずれる、ぐらいの方がニュアンスとしては適切かもしれないです","ts":"1579231739.007800","thread_ts":"1579231602.007300","parent_user_id":"U8R597E9H","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"RUE"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8011e9b8-00d4-41ae-b62d-bc812632aaf5","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"やはりそうですか〜。であれば、かなり厳しいですね。\n一応、LspNextDiagnostic が叩かれた際に diagnostic がくるまでブロックさせて、正しい状態まで待つ。とかはできるんですが、診断の計算も遅い場合があるので現実的ではなさそうです。 :bow:","ts":"1579231910.008000","thread_ts":"1579231602.007300","parent_user_id":"U8R597E9H","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"r1pfG"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"a33a6687-9958-4792-bd63-d3e4da54e62d","type":"message","user":"UGP5AJKU4","text":"はい、厳しいのではと思います…！\n\n\nlspクライアントでキャッシュして頑張るとかブロックするとかすれば誤魔化せそうではあるのかなと考えても、結構キツそうだなという気がしています。。\n\nlsp全体的な処理パフォーマンス上げていく方向の方が多分健全なんだろうなぁと…(何もcontributeしてないので的外れかもしれませんが)","ts":"1579232257.008200","thread_ts":"1579231602.007300","parent_user_id":"U8R597E9H","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"LUJMN"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"5273277a-dfa7-4c8c-9282-8f45b26ba314","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"すみません。\n\n```nmap &lt;buffer&gt; &lt;F12&gt; &lt;plug&gt;(lsp-definition)```\nvim-lspでこういう定義をして、最初の例えばstdoutに飛ぼうとすると飛べるんですが\n\n```use std::io::{stdout, Write};\n\nfn main() {\n    let out = stdout();\n    let mut out = out.lock();\n    out.write_all(b\"Hello\").unwrap();\n    out.flush().unwrap();\n}```\nとんだ先で、例えばstdout_rawでF12を押すと反応せず\n\n```465 #[stable(feature = \"rust1\", since = \"1.0.0\")]\n466 pub fn stdout() -&gt; Stdout {\n467     static INSTANCE: Lazy&lt;ReentrantMutex&lt;RefCell&lt;LineWriter&lt;Maybe&lt;StdoutRaw&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; = Lazy::new();\n468     return Stdout {\n469         inner: unsafe {\n470             INSTANCE.get(stdout_init).expect(\"cannot access stdout during shutdown\")\n471         },\n472     };\n473\n474     fn stdout_init() -&gt; Arc&lt;ReentrantMutex&lt;RefCell&lt;LineWriter&lt;Maybe&lt;StdoutRaw&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; {\n475         // This must not reentrantly access `INSTANCE`\n476         let stdout = match stdout_raw() {\n477             Ok(stdout) =&gt; Maybe::Real(stdout),\n478             _ =&gt; Maybe::Fake,\n479         };\n480         Arc::new(ReentrantMutex::new(RefCell::new(LineWriter::new(stdout))))\n481     }\n482 }```\nLspDefinition を直に実行しようとすると動作します。\nこれ何か設定が足りないのでしょうか。","ts":"1579236234.011300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"k1y"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"2ad2b85e-9ad1-4dd1-8db5-7e55cc79cf3f","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"vimですかね(gvimではなくて)。純粋に端末だと `&lt;F12&gt;` が取れる設定になってないとか、そういう可能性があるかなと。","ts":"1579236514.012700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"J61+"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"bd0ad895-164c-4067-82f4-83fc1e3b5efa","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"まずはファンクションキーじゃなくて `gd` とか普通のキーへのマップから切り分けを始めてはどうかしら","ts":"1579236576.013600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"lzH/"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d749f9a1-fddb-471e-acbe-3c0164ea6975","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あ、","ts":"1579236594.013800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"64m"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"c083557b-e133-4ead-92c6-0ae0a09a943e","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"最初の1回は利いてるのか。","ts":"1579236604.014100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"MP1"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d86e6b5a-3c8a-4da5-a2fb-64823f438014","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"とんだ先のバッファで `:nmap &lt;buffer&gt;` でキーマップが入ってるか確認して、もし入ってたら vim-lsp というかその先のLS実装の問題で、入ってなかったらVim側というかvim-lspの設定のしかたの問題。","ts":"1579236697.015700","edited":{"user":"U06BRP8VD","ts":"1579236707.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Zaxx"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"6801ddc0-0192-49c4-b956-3ee006ad1cc7","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"macのbrewで入れたvimです。\n\n`:nmap <buffer>` を確認したら以下の様になりました。","ts":"1579236993.016200","files":[{"id":"FSG89V541","created":1579236990,"timestamp":1579236990,"name":"スクリーンショット 2020-01-17 13.55.44.png","title":"スクリーンショット 2020-01-17 13.55.44.png","mimetype":"image/png","image_exif_rotation":1,"filetype":"png","pretty_type":"PNG","user":"UEA8T80GY","mode":"hosted","editable":false,"is_external":false,"external_type":"","size":15849,"url":"","url_download":"","url_private":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44.png","url_private_download":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541/download/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44.png","original_h":55,"original_w":748,"thumb_64":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541-c16b092df4/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44_64.png","thumb_80":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541-c16b092df4/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44_80.png","thumb_160":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541-c16b092df4/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44_160.png","thumb_360":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541-c16b092df4/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44_360.png","thumb_360_gif":"","thumb_360_w":360,"thumb_360_h":26,"thumb_480":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T03C4RC8V-FSG89V541-c16b092df4/____________________________2020-01-17_13.55.44_480.png","thumb_480_w":480,"thumb_480_h":35