tion)```","ts":"1579237339.019800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"cSa"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f5ed56fa-2527-4920-84e9-4fa337a7e29a","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"どっちかというと次のプロセスな気がするのでF12か、という問題でもないと思います(koronさんも書いてますが)\n1. lspが有効になったタイミングで、そのバッファに nmap &lt;buffer&gt; &lt;F12&gt;でわりあて\n2. 機能利用で別バッファにjump\n3. 次のバッファではnmap &lt;buffer&gt;で定義されたキーマップはないので、NG\n的な","ts":"1579237353.020200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"njOci"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ee1b72f7-99e8-4d67-93e1-9603005e3226","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"なのでyaegassyさんのみたいな定義すれば大丈夫かも?","ts":"1579237379.020800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"nFH"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"0a59c984-61db-471a-a92d-d4623ee9a559","type":"message","user":"U7TMPGWJ0","text":"それか &lt;buffer&gt; 外しちゃってそれでそのままつぶしちゃうとか\n```nmap &lt;F12&gt; &lt;Plug&gt;(lsp-definition)```","ts":"1579237506.022000","edited":{"user":"U7TMPGWJ0","ts":"1579237609.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"L=s"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"aa12c301-3f0f-48b2-8b4e-d78c6f6f5cfc","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"```au FileType rust nmap <buffer> <F12> <Plug>(lsp-definition)```\nこちらの設定を適用したらキーマップが居ました。","ts":"1579237546.022700","files":[{"id":"FSSEQ0TS9","created":1579237543,"timestamp":1579237543,"name":"スクリーンショット 2020-01-17 14.04.42.png","title":"スクリーンショット 2020-01-17 14.04.42.png","mimetype":"image/png","image_exif_rotation":1,"filetype":"png","pretty_type":"PNG","user":"UEA8T80GY","mode":"hosted","editable":false,"is_external":false,"exte