なかったらVim側というかvim-lspの設定のしかたの問題\nなので設定の方法の問題っぽいですね。","ts":"1579238017.027400","thread_ts":"1579237065.017200","subtype":"thread_broadcast","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"IcK"}],"root":{"client_msg_id":"b0b0f4eb-5f61-4f8f-8990-6da4c58cf596","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"&lt;F12&gt;が不味いのですね。他のキーへ割り当ててみます。","ts":"1579237065.017200","thread_ts":"1579237065.017200","reply_count":1,"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tW4cn"}]}},{"client_msg_id":"defb05ba-7645-45d0-a9e4-2e9f1765e393","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"LSPが有効なfiletypeだったら、っていうのが一番エレガントなんですよね。","ts":"1579238080.028200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"I9in"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"c357dbb5-aea1-4616-8788-7f70ac35eb3b","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"ちょっと理解が難しいんですけど、僕はこんなファイルを置いてます。\nたしかmattnさんが示してくれたやつの改変版。","ts":"1579238215.028300","files":[{"id":"FSSEX4JER","created":1579238214,"timestamp":1579238214,"name":".vim/plugin/lsp-common.vim","title":".vim/plugin/lsp-common.vim","mimetype":"text/plain","image_exif_rotation":0,"filetype":"text","pretty_type":"Plain Text","user":"U06BRP8VD","mode":"snippet","editable":true,"is_external":false,"external_type":"","size":322,"url":"","url_download":"","url_private":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-FSSEX4JER/.vim_plugin_lsp-common.vim","url_private_download":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T03C4RC8V-FSSEX4JER/download/.vim_plugin_lsp-common.vim","original_h":0,"original_w":0,"thumb_64":"","thumb_80":"","thumb_160":"","thumb_360":"","thumb_360_gif":"","thumb_360_w":0,"thumb_360_h":0,"thumb_480":"","thumb_480_w":0,"thumb_480_h":0,"thumb_720":"","thumb_720_w":0,"thumb_720_h":0,"thumb_960":"","thumb_960_w":0,"thumb_960_h":0,"thumb_1024":"","thumb_1024_w":0,"thumb_1024_h":0,"permalink":"https://vim-jp.slack.com/files/U06BRP8VD/FSSEX4JER/.vim_plugin_lsp-common.vim","permalink_public":"https://slack-files.com/T03C4RC8V-FSSEX4JER-db54199e9f","edit_link":"https://vim-jp.slack.com/files/U06BRP8VD/FSSEX4JER/.vim_plugin_lsp-common.vim/edit","preview":"","preview_highlight":"","lines":0,"lines_more":0,"is_public":true,"public_url_shared":false,"channels":null,"groups":null,"ims":null,"initial_comment":{},"comments_count":0,"num_stars":0,"is_starred":false,"shares":{"public":null,"private":null},"display_as_bot":false,"has_rich_preview":false,"username":""}],"upload":true,"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"QGmw"}]},{"client_msg_id":"d646aca2-180a-4e22-a4ad-9ab620163827","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"なるほど、ありがとうございます。これを置いてみます。","ts":"1579238415.028900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"HlaWl"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"3264065d-1483-4880-99a9-4b0fa91aff1c","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"`s:on_lsp_buffer_enabled` 中身をお好みに応じていじってください～","ts":"1579238986.030500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"W3Z"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"b765dbd8-0243-4217-a35c-f8cb6a6aeb91","type":"message","user":"UEA8T80GY","text":"```  \"setlocal omnifunc=lsp#complete\n  \"setlocal signcolumn=yes```\nこの２つがよく分からないですが調べます。\n\n<https://vim-jp.org/vimdoc-ja/autocmd.html#User>\n<https://github.com/vim-jp/issues/issues/142>\n\nありがとうございます。","ts":"1579239218.031700","attachments":[{"fallback":"GitHub: ユーザ定義イベントが欲しい · Issue #142 · vim-jp/issues","id":1,"title":"ユーザ定義イベントが欲しい · Issue #142 · vim-jp/issues","title_link":"https://github.com/vim-jp/issues/issues/142","text":"observable observer な仕組みが欲しい。Vimの挙動に対するイベントではなく、例えば特定アプリのバッファに入った際に MyAppEnter みたいなイベントが作れればプラグインのプラグイン開発が楽になるんじゃなかろうか。 出きれば敷居を低める意味でも autocmd と同じ仕組みで動くと嬉しい。","thumb_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/1051958?s=400&v=4","blocks":null,"service_name":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://a.slack-edge.com/80588/img/unfurl_icons/github.png","thumb_width":400,"thumb_height":400,"from_url":"https://github.com/vim-jp/issues/issues/142","original_url":"https://github.com/vim-jp/issues/issues/142"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ugdo="}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"32b9701c-bb1c-42e2-85b0-958c93ce6c67","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"```setlocal omnifunc=lsp#complete```\n補完を vim-lsp を使う\n```setlocal signcolumn=yes```\nエラーとかが起きた際に左側にサインをだす\nですかね。","ts":"1579239297.032600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"S+tCl"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ebe76e09-a203-4e3a-afac-33cab82a4bd9","type":"message","user":"U78A6ESHM","text":"vim-lsp が有効なバッファにおいて。","ts":"1579239322.032900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"FdQ"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"a58541cd-17c6-4a40-8022-df95c53e9bcd","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"機能はそうなります。","ts":"1579239376.033300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"msc"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"0eb1709c-c827-4d36-971a-02b7cd1332f2","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"Language Server ってプロセスを起動して、初期化メソッドを実行して、と有効になるまでに結構時間がかかるのですよね。","ts":"1579239380.033500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ljz"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"a9439d98-8106-4135-87d5-fda980d6d3bb","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"例えば java の Language Server だと10数秒かかったりするんですが、その起動までの間に F12 が押せちゃうとエラーが起きたりと都合が悪かったりします。","ts":"1579239399.033900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"otM"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1440781a-732c-45ab-b118-16c5c9f01e5a","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"それをイベントを使って遅延で設定させてるんです。","ts":"1579239415.034400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"xyXq"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"758df777-c3fc-4b03-9dd6-8a53375de199","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"あとこれは完全に個人的な意見ですが signcolumn を Language Server 初期化完了時に設定する事で見た目で「あ、Language Server まだ起動してないな」が分かったりします。","ts":"1579239436.034900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"N6GB5"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"81cbb9a3-81b7-4b73-924c-b48ff7cb9242","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"まぁただ僕はどっちもコメントアウトして設定しないようにしてますw","ts":"1579239606.035300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"430Nz"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f5668fec-9946-49ff-b959-20a331c2a476","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"ぼく foldcolumn=2 してるから signcolumn しちゃうと 4カラムつかっちゃうのよねw","ts":"1579239669.037000","thread_ts":"1579239669.037000","reply_count":1,"replies":[{"user":"U06BRP8VD","ts":"1579239713.038200"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"eVa7s"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e769b5da-3808-48cb-9c3b-2ebaeeeaaa7c","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"あー","ts":"1579239681.037300","team":"T03C4RC8